(19,	1,	'2023-07-17 17:11:59',	'2023-07-17 17:11:59',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A good book makes the world an much better place, so we want to empower the people who make books!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Technology has helped more writers become published authors than ever before, but the dream of making a stable, full-time income from writing is still out of reach for far too many. One big reason for this is the fact that existing online book retailers put profits over people. They take too big a cut of authors\' profits and subject authors to unfair business practices.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Vision</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We think authors deserve a marketplace where they\'re in charge. As co-op members, the authors who sell their books on our platform will make business decisions democratically. The platform will take a smaller cut, plus authors will have the option to distribute a portion of the co-op\'s surplus back to themselves as patronage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our marketplace will also strive to offer readers a better browsing experience. Instead of burying search results under ads, we\'ll focus on helping each reader find the right books for them--without ever selling their data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you would like to read more about our motivations and goals, please check out our <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://write\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"write\" target=\"_blank\">project blog</a>!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How the marketplace works</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Right now we are still figuring out how we want to structure our business. We\'re using <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://opencollective.com/write-our-rules\" target=\"_blank\">our page on Open Collective</a> to hold discussions and manage our money. Until we formalize our cooperative, any money we earn will go into our Open Collective account. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The ebooks currently available here are all public domain classics. Readers are welcome to download them for free. If you would like to support our mission, we invite you to \"pay what you want and can\" for any ebook you find here. And if you\'d like to <a href=\"http://the-book-marketplace.local/get-involved/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"2\">get involved</a>, either as an author, reader, or worker, we\'d love to get in touch!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'About Us',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'about',	'',	'',	'2023-07-17 18:08:32',	'2023-07-17 18:08:32',	'',	0,	'http://the-book-marketplace.local/?page_id=19',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
