s\" target=\"_blank\">our page on Open Collective</a> to hold discussions and manage our money. Until we formalize our cooperative, any money we earn will go into our Open Collective account. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The e-books currently available here are all public domain classics. Readers are welcome to download them for free. If you would like to support our mission, we invite you to \"pay what you want and can\" for any e-book you find here. And if you\'d like to <a href=\"http://the-book-marketplace.local/get-involved/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"2\">get involved</a>, either as an author, reader, or worker, we\'d love to get in touch!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'About Us',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'19-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2023-07-17 17:11:59',	'2023-07-17 17:11:59',	'',	19,	'http://the-book-marketplace.local/?p=20',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
