(26,	1,	'2023-07-17 18:33:48',	'2023-07-17 18:33:48',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'re so happy you want to help make the world a better place through an author-and-worker-owned ebook marketplace! There are a few ways you can get involved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For authors and readers</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please sign up for our email list! This way, you\'ll be among the first to know when we\'re ready for indie authors to start selling their own ebooks in the marketplace.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n<script async=\"\" src=\"https://eocampaign1.com/form/2ef9385e-d563-11ed-bdcb-4d5e16350f3b.js\" data-form=\"2ef9385e-d563-11ed-bdcb-4d5e16350f3b\"></script>\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We also encourage you to check out our Open Collective community, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://opencollective.com/write-our-rules\" target=\"_blank\">Write Our Rules</a>. Here, you can help us decide how to spend our budget and make other decisions, such as how we should structure our co-op\'s legal entity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Interested in working with us?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Right now we are looking for volunteers to help with building, promoting, and creating content for our marketplace. Whether you\'re interested in helping us code new features, getting the word out, or curating reading lists, we would love to have you! In the future, we are hoping to offer early volunteers paid jobs and employee ownership. If this sounds good to you, please send a quick introduction to joanna@writeourrules.com.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Get Involved',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'get-involved',	'',	'',	'2023-07-18 03:21:39',	'2023-07-18 03:21:39',	'',	0,	'http://the-book-marketplace.local/?page_id=2