(48,	1,	'2023-07-18 03:36:05',	'2023-07-18 03:36:05',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Johann David Wyss was born in Switzerland on May 28, 1743. A proud father, his goal was to write a book his children could learn from. Today that book, <em>The Swiss Family Robinson, </em>remains popular, though over two centuries have passed since Wysss death on January 11, 1818.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Johann David Wyss',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'johann-david-wyss',	'',	'',	'2023-07-18 03:36:05',	'2023-07-18 03:36:05',	'',	0,	'http://the-book-marketplace.local/?post_type=author-profile&#038;p=48',	0,	'author-profile',	'',	0),
