(76,	1,	'2023-07-18 23:33:15',	'2023-07-18 23:33:15',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Etsuko Inagaki Sugimoto was born in Echigo Province, Japan, just as the countrys feudal system was coming to an end. Her father had been an important samurai, but the changing times brought struggles for her family. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An arranged marriage brought Etsuko to Cincinnati, Ohio, where she gave birth to two daughters. In her later years as a widow, she became an author and a professor at Columbia University in New York City.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Etsuko Sugimoto',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'etsuko-sugimoto',	'',	'',	'2023-07-18 23:33:15',	'2023-07-18 23:33:15',	'',	0,	'http://the-book-marketplace.local/?post_type=author-profile&#038;p=76',	0,	'author-profile',	'',	0),
