(80,	1,	'2023-07-19 17:25:14',	'2023-07-19 17:25:14',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Edgar Poe was born on January 19, 1809 in Boston, Massachusetts. By the time he was just a few years old, his father had abandoned the family, his mother had died, and he had been taken in by a foster family. Despite the rough start, Edgar Allan Poe became a professional author whose poems and stories made him something of a celebrity before his death at the age of forty. Today, he is regarded as one of the greatest American poets of all time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Edgar Allan Poe',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'edgar-allan-poe',	'',	'',	'2023-07-19 17:25:14',	'2023-07-19 17:25:14',	'',	0,	'http://the-book-marketplace.local/?post_type=author-profile&#038;p=80',	0,	'author-profile',	'',	0),
