(84,	1,	'2023-07-19 17:58:02',	'2023-07-19 17:58:02',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Born in London, England, on December 9, 1608, John Milton was completely blind and had fallen into poverty by the time he reached his mid-forties. Despite this, Milton composed some of the most celebrated poetry in the English language, including the epic poem <em>Paradise Lost.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'John Milton',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'john-milton',	'',	'',	'2023-07-19 17:58:02',	'2023-07-19 17:58:02',	'',	0,	'http://the-book-marketplace.local/?post_type=author-profile&#038;p=84',	0,	'author-profile',	'',	0),
